New York Man Admits to Running $6 Million Boiler-Room Scheme

-- B y   T h o m   W e i d l i c h
-- 
2011-10-20T18:59:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/new-york-man-admits-to-running-6-million-boiler-room-scheme.html
A New York man pleaded guilty to
running a boiler-room operation in  Brooklyn  that swindled
customers out of more than $6 million, which the fraudsters
spent on strip clubs, tanning salons, pharmaceuticals and car
washes, prosecutors said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thom Weidlich in New York at 
